text: Cezary Jędrzycki (born 23 January 1969) is a Polish rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw
